			<div class="col-8 centered">
				<h3 class="title">PRIVACY POLICY</h3>
				<p><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,sans-serif"><span style="color:#0c343d">UPDATED 04.10.2018</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Espreso strives for openness and transparency in setting out how and why we hold and process your personal data.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">This privacy policy explicates how we collect, use, share, and transfer your personal data when you use our mobile application <strong>Еспресо &ndash; новости и ТВ </strong>(the &ldquo;Espresso app&rdquo;). </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">By submitting and sharing your information with us you are considered to have explicitly consented processing your personal data in accordance with this policy. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">This Privacy policy specifies:</span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Information that we collect when you interact with the Espreso app</span></span></strong></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">How we use collected information</span></span></strong></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Information we transfer and share with third parties</span></span></strong></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Disclosure of your information </span></span></strong></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Your rights in respect to your information</span></span></strong></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Contact us</span></span></strong></li>
</ul>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Information that we collect when you interact with the Espreso app</span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We continually seek to refine all aspects of the Espreso app in order to make your use efficient, pleasant, and valuable. For this reason, we collect several types of information when you use the Espreso app.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We may ask you to provide us with certain information that can be used to contact or identify you (&quot;<em>Personal Information</em>&quot;). Personal information may include, but is not limited to: your first name and last name, email address, and social media details.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">In addition to this, we may ask you to allow us access your multimedia information available on your devise, such as photo, video, and audio files. We do not normally collect your personal multimedia files, but we use this access to store the Espreso app data in a cache.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Also, we may collect information that your browser sends about your online activity whenever you access the Espreso app by or through your computer, mobile or other device (&quot;<em>Usage Data</em>&quot;).</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">The Usage Data may include information about your device, Internet Protocol address, the sections of the Espreso app that you visit, the date of your visit, the time spent on those sections, behavior on a single section or the entire app, and other diagnostic data. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">In order to deliver you personalized advertising on Android devices we also use an anonymous identifier with respect to your ad tracking preference (<em>the &ldquo;Advertising ID&rdquo;</em>).</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">You can reset your advertising ID or opt out of interest-based ads at any time from the Google Settings app. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to track the activity on the Espreso app.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Cookies are files with small amount of data that include anonymous unique identifiers, such as your session cookies, preference and other settings cookies, security cookies. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">You can instruct your browser to refuse all cookies or to indicate when a cookie is being sent. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Sometimes the Espreso app may contain links to third party sites and services. Before following an external link we strongly recommend you to ensure that you read the privacy policy shown on these sites. We do not bear the responsibility for the privacy policy and/or the content of these sites. Likewise, if you are directed to the Espresso app from a third party we are not responsible for the privacy policy of the third party. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">When you sign in to the Espreso app using your social media login details, you give permission to Facebook, Twitter or Google Plus to share with us certain aspects of your profile if you have made these public in your Facebook/Twitter/Google Plus profile. This may include your first and last name, email address, age range, link to your Facebook/Twitter/Google Plus profile</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">,</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626"> and profile picture if you have one. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We will then use this information to identify you and allow you to send questions to editors through the Espresso app.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">If the Espreso app is removed from your Facebook/Twitter and/or Google Plus settings, we will no longer have access to this data. However, we will still have the information that we received when you first set up your Espreso account using your Facebook/Twitter/Google login.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">When you authorise on the Espreso app and vote in our interactive polls or questionnaires, we will then include your vote into the statistics and make the statistics available to public via ESPRESO TV broadcast and via </span></span><a href="https://espreso.tv/"><span style="font-size:12.0pt">our site</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">. Please note that under no circumstances do we share your Personal information when counting your vote. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Information that we do not track</span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We do not knowingly or intentionally track sensitive personal information from individuals, and you must not submit sensitive personal information to us.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">If, however, you inadvertently transmit sensitive information to us, you give your consent to processing that sensitive personal information for the purposes of deleting it.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">How we use collected information </span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">The main reasons why we collect and use information provided when you access and use the Espreso app are as follows:</span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">T</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">o communicate with you</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626"> when you come into contact or request that we come into contact with you through the Espresso app.</span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">To personalise our services for you</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">, saving your settings, fixing your preferences, recognising you when you sign in on different devices.</span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">To display personalised advertising</span></span></strong> <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">as well as to measure how efficient our online adverts are for you.</span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">To provide analysis</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626"> so that we can readily identify any areas of potential enhancement of the Espreso app and improve your experience with us.</span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">To comply with applicable laws </span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">and regulations.</span></span></li>
</ul>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Information we transfer and share with third parties</span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We retain your personal information and other data for only as long as we need to perform our services in accordance with legal requirements. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We transfer the data that you provide us with while using the Espreso app, including Personal information, to Ukraine and process it there with accordance with the Ukrainian legislation. Please take into consideration that the data protection laws in Ukraine may differ than those from your jurisdiction. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Your consent to this Privacy policy followed by your submission of such information represents your agreement to that transfer. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We take all reasonable steps to ensure that your data is treated securely and no transfer of your Personal information takes place, except as described in this Privacy policy.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">For the purpose of analysing the use of the Espreso app and understanding the performance of the Espreso app, we use a web analytics service Google Analytics. Google uses the data collected to track and monitor the use of the Espreso app and might share it with other Google services. Google may use the collected data to contextualise and personalise the ads of its own advertising network. For more information on the privacy practices of Google, please visit the Google Privacy &amp; Terms </span></span><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=en&amp;gl=ZZ"><span style="font-size:12.0pt">web page</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Furthermore, when we send you a push notification, these are delivered by marketing platform </span></span><a href="https://onesignal.com/" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">onesignal.com</span></span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">. As part of this service, certain information is recorded to enable delivering the best notification experience. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="color:#262626">For more information on the privacy practices of </span><a href="https://onesignal.com/" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">onesignal.com</span></span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626"> please visit their Data Collection </span></span><a href="https://documentation.onesignal.com/docs/data-collected-by-the-onesignal-sdk"><span style="font-size:12.0pt">web page</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Disclosure of data </span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We may disclose your Personal information in the good faith that such disclosure is necessary to comply with a legal obligation, take reasonable preventive measures or investigate possible lawbreaking, protect the personal safety of users of the Espreso app or the public.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Security of data </span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">We take the security of your data seriously. We are committed to hold your Personal information and other data secure. Remember, though, that the internet is a global environment and no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage can guarantee total security. </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Your rights in respect to your information</span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">You can contact us with regard to the following rights in relation to your personal data:</span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Where you have provided us with consent to use your Personal information, you can withdraw this at any time.</span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Where applicable, you may have a right to receive a machine-readable copy of your Personal information.</span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">You also have the right to ask us to delete your Personal information or restrict our use of your information. There may be exceptions to the right to erasure for specific legal reasons which, if relevant, we will set out for you in response to your request. </span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Where applicable, you have the right to object to processing of your Personal information for certain purposes.</span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">You have other rights congruent with the requirements of the law of Ukraine.</span></span></li>
</ul>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">If you want to make any of these requests, please contact </span></span><a href="mailto:developer@espreso.tv"><span style="font-size:12.0pt">developer@espreso.tv</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt">. </span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#262626">Contact us for details about how we use your Personal information</span></span></strong></p>

